              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "50g caster sugar"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2 tbsp golden syrup"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "200ml milk"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Melt the chocolate and butter in a bain marie. Stir in the sugar and syrup until dissolved (I put less in than is recommended above as the mousse is so sweet I think it needs to be a bit more bitter to balance it, then pour in the milk and continue to cook stirring often until the sauce thickens."
                  }
                ]
              }
